name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
notes: ***1ST DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA DOSIS DE PFIZER!!!! The vaccination clinic will take place at Holy Redeemer Church in Parish/Church Hall building. Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your shoulder. Vaccinations at this site are reserved for people who live and/or work in Washington State. All individuals 16 and over are eligible to get vaccinated. Those under 18 must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via video/phone call or paper format. La clínica de vacunación se llevara a cabo en la Iglesia del Santo Redentor (Holy Redeemer) en el edificio del Salón Parroquial de la iglesia. Se requieren máscaras. Por favor, use ropa que permita acceso a su brazo. Las vacunas en este sitio están reservadas para las personas que viven o trabajan en el estado de Washington. Todas las personas mayores de 16 años son elegibles para vacunarse. Los menores de 18 años deben estar acompañados por un padre/tutor o deben obtener el consentimiento de los padres por video/llamada telefónica o en papel. ***1ST DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA DOSIS DE PFIZER!!!!
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Consistent Care Services- COVID Vaccine Site
notes:
***This is a clinic for 1st or 2nd doses of the Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine. *** All patients 12 years old and older can register regardless of phase. (If 12-17 years old must be with a parent or guardian or have parental/guardian consent) Vaccinations at the Consistent Care Services COVID Vaccine Clinic are by appointment only. The clinic is located at 1235 N. Post St., Spokane WA 99201. The clinic is located upstairs in suite 201. There is elevator access or stairs. Enter the building at the time of your appointment only. 
***Residents of ANY state are now eligible for the vaccine, but you still must have photo ID***
***Parking is free on the West side of the building only in stalls 14-55. Please do not come to your appointment if you are sick*** 
***Please no outside food or drinks***  
*VERY IMPORTANT*
***Please complete all the insurance/Medicare/Medicaid information when registering online for your appointment to avoid filling it out at the clinic***
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
